@5007  = ~inquisitor~
@5008  = ~Inquisitor of Helm~
@5009  = ~INQUISITOR OF HELM: The Inquisitor is dedicated to the god Helm, with the goal of finding and eliminating practitioners of evil magic and defeating the forces of darkness.

Advantages:
- May cast Minor Globe of Invulnerability once per day at 5th level, and twice per day at 10th level.
- May cast Breach once per day at 7th level, and twice per day at 13th level.
