- May cast Lathander's Restoration once per day at 12th level, which heals the recipient of all physical, mental, and other ailments.
- Springlords of Lathander are immune to level drain.

BOON OF LATHANDER: This spell lasts for ten rounds. It gives the recipient a +1 bonus to attack and damage rolls, a +1 bonus to all Saving Throws, and 1 extra attack per round. It also protects the recipient from level drain.

Restrictions:
