~
@5059  = ~stormrider of talos~
@5060  = ~Stormrider of Talos~
@5061  = ~STORMRIDER OF TALOS: Talos is the evil god of storms, destruction, and rebellion. Clerics of the Stormlord warn that Talos must be appeased or he will rain destruction upon the land.

