@5262  = ~mistwalker of leira~
@5263  = ~Mistwalker of Leira~
@5264  = ~MISTWALKER OF LEIRA: Leira is the goddess of deception and illusion. She was supposedly slain under mysterious circumstances during the Avatar crisis, but at least one sect of her worshippers, the Mistwalkers, continue to receive divine power. Lies are their currency, illusion is their tool. 

